metadata.name: Future Maria Clara
metadata.description: "Futuristic Maria Clara" is a bold and daring piece that embodies the fusion of tradition and innovation. This painting portrays the iconic Philippine figure, Maria Clara, in a futuristic setting, showcasing her as a symbol of strength and resilience in the face of rapid technological advancement. Creating a dynamic interplay between the past and the future, highlighting the timelessness of cultural heritage even in the face of change.
